201
00:10:33.767 --> 00:10:35.135
<i>Just what Harrison needs.</i>

202
00:10:35.235 --> 00:10:36.804
<i>a good cop.</i>

203
00:10:36.904 --> 00:10:39.139
And you already noted
that the shower liner

