hotel. would not hide blood.

223
00:11:27.454 --> 00:11:28.889
<i>Only oxygen bleach</i>

224
00:11:28.989 --> 00:11:29.689
<i>-would do that.</i>
-Only oxygen bleach

225
00:11:29.790 --> 00:11:30.690
would do that.

226
00:11:30.791 --> 00:11:32.492
Which suggests

227
00:11:32.592 --> 00:11:34.544
